{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/350","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/350/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/350/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/350/events","html_url":"https://github.com/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/350","id":1727291,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUxNzI3Mjkx","number":350,"title":"assertEquals(3, acos(8)) returns true","user":{"login":"wolfsage","id":643871,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY0Mzg3MQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/643871?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/wolfsage","html_url":"https://github.com/wolfsage","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wolfsage/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wolfsage/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wolfsage/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wolfsage/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wolfsage/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wolfsage/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wolfsage/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wolfsage/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/wolfsage/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2011-09-23T21:51:58Z","updated_at":"2011-09-26T08:03:15Z","closed_at":"2011-09-26T08:03:15Z","author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"The assertEquals() functions returns true when one of the arguments is NAN.\n\nThis is because the code that compares numbers does this:\n\n```\n\n    protected function numericComparison($a, $b)\n    {\n        if ($this->delta === FALSE) {\n            return ($a == $b);\n        } else {\n            return (abs($a - $b) <= $this->delta);\n        }\n    }\n\n```\n\nbut delta defaults to 0, so abs(NAN-3) <= 0 returns true.\n\nExample test case:\n\n```\n\n<?php\nrequire_once 'PHPUnit/Framework.php';\n\nclass ex_Test extends PHPUnit_Framework_TestCase {\n        public function test_NAN() {\n                $var = acos(8);\n                $this->assertEquals(3, $var, 'THIS SHOULD FAIL');\n        }\n}\n\n```\n\nThis also affects assertNotEquals()\n","closed_by":{"login":"sebastianbergmann","id":25218,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI1MjE4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/25218?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann","html_url":"https://github.com/sebastianbergmann","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/sebastianbergmann/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/350/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https:/